com.microsoft.office.sfb.appsdk

Interface Participant

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Observable

    public interface Participant
extends Observable
    This interface represents a participant (local or remote) in the conversation. It contains a set of services that respresent each aspect of this participant's communication into the conversation: e.g. a service for chat messaging, a service for audio, a service for video etc.

    • Field Detail

      • ROLE_CHANGED_PROPERTY_ID

        static final int ROLE_CHANGED_PROPERTY_ID
        Property ID for notifying that role of the participant has changed. Subscribers will be notified via the onPropertyChanged method on the Observable.OnPropertyChangedCallback interface with this property id. E.g. callback.onPropertyChanged(ROLE_CHANGED_PROPERTY_ID). Clients are expected to call the getRole method to get the new role.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • STATE_CHANGED_PROPERTY_ID

        static final int STATE_CHANGED_PROPERTY_ID
        Property ID for notifying that state of the participant in the meeting has changed. Subscribers will be notified via the onPropertyChanged method on the Observable.OnPropertyChangedCallback interface with this property id. E.g. callback.onPropertyChanged(ROLE_CHANGED_PROPERTY_ID). Clients are expected to call the getState method to get the new state.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
